APK PLACEHOLDER FILE

This is a placeholder for the actual Android APK file.

To build the real APK:
1. Install Android Studio
2. Open the android-app folder in Android Studio
3. Build > Generate Signed Bundle/APK
4. Select APK
5. Follow the signing process
6. Replace this file with the generated APK

The APK will be approximately 8-10MB when built with optimizations.
